title: Kennedy.2015.05.07.WS.SDTV.x264-XAiO
description:
Kennedy talks more Delategate in her monologue.

JIMMY FAILLA, JOHN TIERNEY, and NOELLE NIKPOUR discuss Pentagon employee use of government issued credit cards to gamble and get hookers in Atlantic City. Apple Watch gives parents ability to track children.

RYAN MAURO talks about the terrorist attack on Free Speech event in Texas and ISIS attempts to claim credit for it.

JUDGE ANDREW NAPOLITANO is interviewed about the recent ruling that declared the provisions within the Patriot Act that allowed the NSA to do mass spying illegal.

The panel returns to discuss dad bods, and McDonalds using kale.

ALEX GARLAND talks about his movie "Ex-Machina".
